iragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Redis：7.x</li><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 缓存</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 消息队列</li></ul><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Nacos：2.2.0（配置中心、注册中心）</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Sentinel（分布式流量治理组件）<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">java -Dserver.port=8888 -Dcsp.sentinel.dashboard.server=localhost:8888 -Dproject.name=sentinel-dashboard -jar sentinel-dashboard.jar</code></li></ul><h3 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\">2、项目结构</h3><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">2.1 core</h4><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">项目公共模块包括：</p><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">common</code>:公共类库</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">security</code>:公共权限验证模块</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">module</code>数据库操作层</li></ul><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">2.2 open-api2</h4><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">早期版本的各个平台的微服务，包括</p><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• dou-api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• jd-api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• pdd-api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• tao-api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• wei-api</li></ul><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">后期这些微服务统一合并到open-api</strong></p><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">2.3 open-api-sdk</h4><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">各电商开放平台接口sdk</p><h3 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\">3、运行说明</h3><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">3.1、启动环境</h4><ol style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">1. 启动MySQL8</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">2. 启动Redis7</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">3. 启动Nacos2.2.0</li></ol><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">3.2、启动服务(项目)</h4><h5 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">3.2.1 单体版本</h5><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">启动app项目即可，注意修改application.yml配置</strong></p><h5 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">3.2.2 微服务版本</h5><ol style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">1. 启动业务微服务<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">api</code>父项目下：（sys-api、oms-api、wms-api、open-api、op、gateway微服务）</li></ol><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">3.3、运行前端</h4><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">不管后端是微服务版本还是单体版本，前端vue项目都是一样的</strong></p><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Nodejs版本：v16.20.0</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 进入<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">vue</code>文件夹</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 运行<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">npm install</code> </li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 运行<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">npm run dev</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 浏览网页<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">http://localhost</code></li></ul><h3 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\">4、前端部署</h3><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">4.1 打包</h4><h5 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">前端打包</h5><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">pnpm run build:prod</code><br><span style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #576b95\">README.md</span></p><h4 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">4.2 Nginx配置</h4><pre class=\"hljs code__pre\" style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin: 10px 8px; padding: 0 !important;\"><span class=\"mac-sign\" style=\"display: flex; padding: 10px 14px 0;\" hidden=\"\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"45px\" height=\"13px\" viewBox=\"0 0 450 130\">\r\n    <ellipse cx=\"50\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(220,60,54)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(237,108,96)\"></ellipse>\r\n    <ellipse cx=\"225\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(218,151,33)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(247,193,81)\"></ellipse>\r\n    <ellipse cx=\"400\" cy=\"65\" rx=\"50\" ry=\"52\" stroke=\"rgb(27,161,37)\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"rgb(100,200,86)\"></ellipse>\r\n  </svg></span><code class=\"language-\" style=\"display: -webkit-box; padding: 0.5em 1em 1em; overflow-x: auto; text-indent: 0; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: Menlo, Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, monospace; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; white-space: nowrap;\">#&nbsp;上传文件至远程服务器<br>将打包生成在&nbsp;`dist`&nbsp;目录下的文件拷贝至&nbsp;`/opt/qihangerp/nginx/dist`&nbsp;目录<br><br>#&nbsp;nginx.cofig&nbsp;配置<br>server&nbsp;{<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;listen&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;80;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;server_name&nbsp;&nbsp;localhost;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;location&nbsp;/&nbsp;{<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#root&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/opt/qihangerp/nginx/dist;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;root&nbsp;/usr/share/nginx/html;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;index&nbsp;&nbsp;index.html&nbsp;index.htm;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;try_files&nbsp;$uri&nbsp;$uri/&nbsp;/index.html;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;#&nbsp;反向代理配置<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;location&nbsp;/prod-api/&nbsp;{<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;proxy_set_header&nbsp;Host&nbsp;$http_host;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;proxy_set_header&nbsp;X-Real-IP&nbsp;$remote_addr;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;proxy_set_header&nbsp;REMOTE-HOST&nbsp;$remote_addr;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;proxy_set_header&nbsp;X-Forwarded-For&nbsp;$proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;proxy_pass&nbsp;http://127.0.0.1:8088/;&nbsp;#&nbsp;替换成你的后端网关API地址<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>}</code></pre>\r\n    \r\n  \r\n        \r\n      \r\n      \r\n    </section><p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>', 1, NULL, '1736477799', 1, 'xitongjieshao', 99, 0);
INSERT INTO `sys_help` VALUES (4, '项目起源', '<p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><section style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px\"><h2 style=\" text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold;margin-transform: translateY( 0\">项目背景</h2><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system)-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">启航电商ERP可以说是我这五年以来的工作经验成果。</strong></p><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">公司从2019年踏入电商以来，一直都是由我组建和带领一帮技术人员从零开始建设了一套完全适应公司业务需要的电商ERP系统，包括WMS仓库系统、OMS订单处理系统、财务系统、直播运营系统等子系统组成。主要功能模块包括：采购模块、出入库模块、订单发货模块、网店订单管理模块、电子面单打印模块。公司ERP对接了批批网、1688、蘑菇街、淘宝天猫、拼多多、抖店、快手小店平台。</p>公司应用场景一：抖店直播<br><figure style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; display: block; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://foruda.gitee.com/images/1736428717987299032/9716eb3b_119616.png\" title=\"null\" alt=\"\"><figcaption style=\" text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\"></figcaption></figure><h2 style=\" text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">开源</h2><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">2022年由于疫情影响，公司出现资金问题，被迫关闭电商业务。我也就失业了，2023年我来到一家做三维技术为主的技术项目公司，在公司工作期间接触到了很多新行业知识，也认识了很多新行业资深人士。让我深深感受到行业知识也是个壁垒，所以萌生了继续做电商行业开源系统的想法。系统开源之初，目的就是锻炼个人技术能力和展示自己过往工作经验。<br>没有想到的是，开源之后受到很多朋友们的关注、鼓励、支持，甚至很多朋友认为我的大佬。这也增强了我继续开源的信心，我相信这大家的支持下，我会把电商ERP系统继续开源下去，并且做成一个好用稳定高效的新型电商系统。</p><h2 style=\" text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">关于我</h2><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">本人具有十年电商行业系统开发经验，开发过的部分产品有：</p><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 波特商城线上线下交易系统（POS收银、在线商城）</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 华贸城在线电商平台（小商品在线电商）</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 微店网（综合在线电商平台，供应商入驻）</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 华衣电商ERP系统（对接淘宝、拼多多、抖店直播）</li></ul><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">等大型电商系统，拥有丰富的电商行业实战经验。</p>有收入才能更好地有动力继续开源，如果项目有帮助到您，请支持一下（接受捐助）。<br><figure style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; display: block; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://foruda.gitee.com/images/1736478911979509866/83c5a710_119616.jpeg\" title=\"微信收款码.jpg\" alt=\"输入图片说明\"><figcaption style=\" text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\">输入图片说明</figcaption></figure><figure style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\"><img style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; display: block; margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em; border-radius: 4px;\" src=\"https://foruda.gitee.com/images/1736478929729507011/80442f70_119616.jpeg\" title=\"支付宝收款码.jpg\" alt=\"输入图片说明\"><figcaption style=\" text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888\">输入图片说明</figcaption></figure>\r\n    \r\n  \r\n        \r\n      \r\n      \r\n    </section><p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>', 1, '1736477070', '1736479094', 1, 'xiangmuqiyuan', 99, 0);
INSERT INTO `sys_help` VALUES (5, '开发计划', '开发计划', 1, '1736477481', '1736479159', 1, 'kaifajihua', 99, 0);
INSERT INTO `sys_help` VALUES (6, '如何获取授权', '<p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><section style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px\"><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;margin-transform: translateY( 0\"> 启航电商ERP系统自2023年开源以来，在大家的帮助与支持下，目前已经升级到了2.0版本。2.0版本是一个完整开箱即用的电商ERP系统，经历过一年多的迭代优化和客户使用验证。开发者可以直接部署即可使用。接下来我们会继续优化和完善项目，我们的目标是做一个标准稳定、高效可靠的电商订单处理核心业务系统，近期的方向和目标是：</p><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system)-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 1、继续完善ERP系统和OMS系统功能的开发，计划接入更多电商平台包括跨境电商平台；</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 2、推出开放平台SDK，帮助开发者快速对接主流电商平台接口，省去了每个平台都需要对接的时间成本；</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 3、上线帮助文档网站，包括：API接口、部署文档等等，帮助开发者扩展和对接其他内部电商系统；</li></ul><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">同时启航电商ERP系统作者推出以下服务，帮助大家快速部署或二次开发。</p><h3 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\">服务一：SDK授权服务，有官方授权，安心省心。</h3><h3 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\">服务二：开源系统部署服务，作者团队快速部署，帮助非开发者也能很方便地使用上开源电商系统。</h3><h3 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\">服务三：商业版服务，购买商业版本，提供完整的售后运维服务。</h3><h3 style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\">服务四：电商系统定制开发服务，作者团队精通各种电商系统，可以快速帮您定制开发各种电商系统，并且提供完善的售后服务。</h3><p style=\" text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\">感谢大家的支持！希望能为大家创造价值！有需要的朋友们联系作者。</p>\r\n    \r\n  \r\n        \r\n      \r\n      \r\n    </section><p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>', 2, '1739166692', '1739166891', 1, 'shouquan', 99, 0);
INSERT INTO `sys_help` VALUES (7, '架构说明', '<p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><section style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px\"><h2 id=\"0\" style=\" text-align: center; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; display: table; padding: 0 0.2em; margin: 4em auto 2em; color: #fff; background: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold;margin-top: 0\" data-heading=\"true\">项目架构</h2><h3 id=\"1\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">1、开发环境级组件</h3><h4 id=\"2\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">1.1 开发环境</h4><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Jdk：17</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Nodejs：v16.20.0</li></ul><h4 id=\"3\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">1.2、存储及中间件</h4><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• MySQL8</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Redis：7.x</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Kafka(消息队列)</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-sy