-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">oms-api</code><br>oms主功能微服务，主要功能包括：</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 队列消息处理（订单消息、退款消息）</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 订单接口</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 退款接口</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 店铺接口</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• <code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">open-api</code><br>各开放平台微服务</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 淘宝开放平台接口api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 京东开放平台接口api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 抖店开放平台接口api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 拼多多开放平台接口api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 微信小店开放平台接口api</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 快手小店开放平台接口api</li></ul><h3 id=\"8\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.2; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15.400000000000002px; padding-left: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #0F4C81; margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0; color: #3f3f3f; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">3、运行说明</h3><h4 id=\"9\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">3.1、启动环境</h4><ol style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">1. 启动MySQL8</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">2. 启动Redis7</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">3. 启动Sentinel1.8.7控制台(可以不需要)<br><code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">java -Dserver.port=8888 -Dcsp.sentinel.dashboard.server=localhost:8888 -Dproject.name=sentinel-dashboard -jar sentinel-dashboard.jar</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">4. 启动Nacos（注册中心）</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">5. 启动Kafka（消息队列）<br><code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">启动KRaft模式kafka</code></li><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 0 进入kafka解压目录</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 1 生成UUID<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-storage.bat random-uuid</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 2 格式化<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-storage.bat format -t 7HZlayMPQdmMVcXnsFk8dg -c config\\kraft\\server.properties</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 3 启动<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-server-start.bat config\\kraft\\server.properties</code></li></ul></ol><h4 id=\"10\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">3.2、导入数据库</h4><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 创建数据库<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">qihang-oms</code></li><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 导入数据库结构：sql脚本<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">docs\\qihang-oms.sql</code></li></ul></ul><h4 id=\"11\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">3.3、启动服务(项目)</h4><ol style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">1. 启动开放平台微服务（<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">open-api</code>）</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">2. 启动<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">sys-api</code>、<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">oms-api</code>微服务</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">3. 启动微服务网关（<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">gateway</code>）</li></ol><h4 id=\"12\" style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 2em 8px 0.5em; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\" data-heading=\"true\">3.4、运行前端</h4><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• Nodejs版本：v16.20.0</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 进入<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">vue</code>文件夹</li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 运行<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">npm install</code> </li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 运行<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">npm run dev</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 浏览网页<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">http://localhost:88</code></li></ul>\r\n    \r\n  \r\n        \r\n      \r\n      \r\n    </section><p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>', 1, '1736475081', '1742960657', 1, 'jiagou', 99, 0);
INSERT INTO `sys_help` VALUES (9, '新鲜出炉kafka4.0 windows 部署教程', ' <p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p><section style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px\"><p style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f;margin-top: 0\">kafka4.0 windows 部署</p><p style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 1.5em 8px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f\"><strong style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: inherit; color: #0F4C81; font-weight: bold\">Kafka没有专门为Windows制作独立包，但是在windows下可以直接下载 kafka_2.13-4.0.0.tgz进行部署</strong></p><ul style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f\"><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 下载：<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">https://kafka.apache.org/downloads</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 生成UUID：<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-storage.bat random-uuid</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 格式化：<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-storage.bat format --standalone -t rYfhz8FaQqGtKRSHhMFTmg -c config/server.properties</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 启动：<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-server-start.bat config\\server.properties</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 创建topic：<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-topics.bat --create --topic test-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 启动生产者：<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-console-producer.bat --topic test-topic --bootstrap-server localhost:9092</code></li><li style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: -1em; display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f\">• 启动消费者：<code style=\" text-align: left; line-height: 1.75; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27,31,35,.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px\">bin\\windows\\kafka-console-consumer.bat --topic test-topic --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092</code></li></ul>\r\n    \r\n  \r\n        \r\n      \r\n      \r\n    </section><p style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>', 6, '1743212672', NULL, 1, 'kafka4.0bushu', 99, 0);
